<Task version="1.4" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/windows/2004/02/mit/task">
  <RegistrationInfo>
    <Description>Daily dream-crystallize for supervisor domain (manual stub v0.1, awaits DO-SUPERVISOR-002 factory CLI extension). Aggregates last 24h updates from archive/, outbox/, internal/circular/. Yasu review priority: LOW (green marker).</Description>
